  <h1 class="advertorial__headline">I Spent $4,217 on Back Pain Products. Every Single One Failed for the Same Reason.</h1>

  <p class="advertorial__text">I counted them last Tuesday night.</p>

  <p class="advertorial__text">Eleven products. Stuffed into my nightstand drawer like a graveyard of broken promises. TENS units. Copper wraps. Creams. Massage cushions. A $130 vibrating pillow that made my sciatica worse.</p>

  <p class="advertorial__text"><strong>Total: $4,217.</strong> And that's before the cortisone shots, the physical therapy, and the prescriptions.</p>

  <p class="advertorial__text">Every single one failed. And until two months ago, I had no idea why.</p>

